reviewText: Some of the best 3D I've seen.  I thought the story was good.  I'm not sure why so many other people thought it sucked.  I guess I will always be an outsider in my thinking.  Solid entertainment.  Amazing action scenes, funny, and visually stunning.

I enjoyed this film immensely. It was very action packed and I didn't really notice many slow spots. I appreciated the concept that we (humans from earth) are not the only intelligent beings in the universe. I loved that the beings from all forms of life were able to work together for common goals, especially those for the good.
